
Styrsignaler:

uPC
    000     +1
    001     op addr
    010     A a-mod addr
    011     B a-mod addr
    100     jmp
    101     jmp on Z
    111     0

PC
    0       PC (nothing)
    1       +1

uCount
    00      uCounter + 1
    01      Z = uCounter >= limit
    11      uCounter = 0

mem1
    00      nothing
    01      read
    10      write

mem2
    00      nothing
    01      read
    10      write

mem3
    00      nothing
    01      read
    10      write

graphic
    1 bit (0 bit?)
        reset (sätt neutral färg när vi rensar minnet, kanske kan ledas till `not (P1 or P2)` om vi ej rensar status före)


buss_in
    PC
    OP (-> IR)
    AR B (+ PC)
    FIFO
    I/O
    3 bit

buss_out
    nothing
    PC
    M1
    M2
    OP
    ALU B (-> PC)
    IR
    FIFO
    4 bit


FIXME!
Kontrollera signalerna under
FIXME!


ADR
    3 bit select from
        M1
        M2
        AR A
        AR B
        PC
        buss
        nothing

ALU (both)
    3bit control function
        -1
        +1
        load
        add
        sub
        cmp
        nothing

ALU A
    2 bit select input
        M1
        M2
        PC
        buss

ALU B
    2 bit select input
        M1
        M2
        PC
        buss

FIFO
    2bit
        read
        write
        nothing

    3 bit P1 function
        incr read
        zero read
        incr write
        zero write
        nothing

    3 bit P2 function
        incr read
        zero read
        incr write
        zero write
        nothing

    1bit
        change player
        nothing

M1
    3 bit choose in
        AR A
        AR B
        M2
        buss
        nothing

M2
    3 bit choose in
        AR A
        AR B
        M1
        buss
        nothing

Totalt
    2 rw OP mem
    2 rw op1 mem
    2 rw op1 mem
    4 buss in
    4 buss out
    3 uPC
    2 uCount
    1 PC
    3 ADR
    3 ALU (both)
    2 ALU A input
    2 ALU B input
    7 FIFO
    3 M1
    3 M2

    43 styrsignaler

    + 8 bit hoppaddress

    51 bit

